div.p:
AS in an Ouen or fornace, the fire doth quickly consume the wood which is put therein;
                     Psalm. 21.9. so the wicked in the day wherein God will shew foorth his anger,
                     Mala. 4.1. shal quickly be consumed. Or rather with what facilitie and speed, strawe or stubble is consumed in the heating of an Ouen, with the like the wicked shall be destroyed.
